rank.name: top
rank.desc_long:
Displays the top ranking depending on your arguments
You can choose between your rank within the server or globally!
You can also shorten arguments like the examples below.

my.name: my
my.desc_long:
Displays the your ranking depending on your arguments
You can choose between your rank within the server or globally!
You can also shorten arguments like the examples below.

money.name: money
money.desc_short: How much cowoncy do you own?
money.desc_long: You can check your cowoncy balance. You earn more cowoncy by saying owo, dailies, and voting!

give.name: give
give.desc_long: Send some cowoncy to other users! command must contain a @mention and a number.

daily.name: daily
daily.desc_long: Grab your daily cowoncy every 24H! Daily streaks will give you extra cowoncy!

vote.name: vote
vote.desc_long: Vote for OwO bot every 24H on discordbots.org to gain cowoncy! Streaks will give more cowoncy!

zoo.name: zoo
zoo.desc_long: Displays your zoo! Catch some animals with 'owo hunt'!

hunt.name: hunt
hunt.desc_long:
Hunt for some animals for your zoo!
Higher ranking animals are harder to get!

slots.name: slots
slots.desc_long: Bet your money on the slot machine! Earn up to 10x your money!

lottery.name: lottery
lottery.desc_long:
Bet your money in the lottery! The more money you bet, the higher the chance!
Lottery ends 12am PST everyday

b8.name: 8b
b8.desc_long: Ask a question and get an answer!

define.name: define
define.desc_long: Grabs a definition from Urban Dictionary~

gif.name: gif
gif.desc_long: Grabs a gif/pic with the given type. To list all types, type 'owo gif'. Most types may not work for pic command.

pet.name: pet
pet.desc_long:
Pet/hug/punch/etc someone!
Related emotes are down below!

shrug.name: shrug
shrug.desc_long:
Shrug, cry, pout, etc! 
Related commands below!

feedback.name: feedback
feedback.desc_long: Sends a feedback to an admin! Admins will reply back and maybe with a lil gift~
example: owo feedback I love this bot!

link.name: link
link.desc_long: Gives you a link to add OwO bot to another server!

guildlink.name: guildlink
guildlink.desc_long: Gives you a link to come join our discord server! Come for some help or extra cowoncy ;)

ping.name: ping
ping.desc_long: Gives you the bot's average ping!

help.name: help
help.desc_long: Gives you the list of commands or add a command at the end to describe a command!

disable.name: disable
disable.desc_long: Enable/Disable a command for this channel! Only users with the MANAGE_CHANNELS permission can use this command

rep.name: rep
rep.desc_short: Give a cookie to a user!
rep.desc_long:
Gives a cookie to a user! You can only send one per day!
You can also give cookies to bots!

battle.name: battle
battle.desc_long:
Use your animal to fight against other players! As you fight, the will level to become stronger!
They will also level up if someone fights against your pet!
Feel free to add as many pets and check their status with 'owo pets'!
You can also rename your animals!

pets.name: pets
pets.desc_long:
Displays your current pets! These pets can fight other users with 'owo battle'! You can only add pets from your current zoo.
All pets have different stats and can be renamed!
example: owo pets set lion lion boi

sell.name: sell
sell.desc_long: Sell animals in your zoo! It will sell all but one if you don't specify count. Selling animals will NOT affect your zoo score

translate.name: translate
translate.desc_long: Translate a given message to a specific language. The default language will be english. Use 'owo listlang' to see available languages

listlang.name: listlang
listlang.desc_long: List all languages for translate command

shop.name: shop
shop.desc_long:
Buy some items to upgrade your pets!
You can describe each item with 'owo describe {id}'
